      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SON OF RUPEE (2) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 2 lengths behind Moonshine Mirage in 25.78 and recording a new PB here. Expected to go close if runs up to latest. SHE PICKED IT (1) is better than last start when fourth (26.04) in a Grade 6 at this track over 457m. The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and can measure up. GUS THE GANGSTER (6) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start sixth (26.58) at this track. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Should be about the mark. ZIPPING MUSETTI (7) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
